data.description: B E A UTIFUL new home on the market and ready for new owners! Located in the heart of Jacksonville, NC and just minutes away from shopping, dining, base access, and entertainment. When you walk in you will be greeted by a nice formal dining room to your left and a large living room to your right. 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half bathrooms. Tree lined yard and large deck as well as a privacy fenced back yard and one car garage brings all the must have's in a home together! Don't wait, call and schedule your own showing today before its to late!
